Company Overview

Acefone is a cloud communications platform provider (CPaaS + CCaaS) that enables businesses to manage voice, messaging, and customer interactions through scalable cloud infrastructure.

Acefone provides communication infrastructure, automation tools, and contact center solutions that help businesses handle inbound and outbound customer communication efficiently.

The platform is designed to support:
- Customer support teams
- Sales teams
- Contact centers
- Customer experience teams
- IT and operations leaders

Acefone Products

- Contact Center Studio
- Interactions Hub (Omnichannel Workspace)
- API Connect (APIs Hub)
- Campaigns (Multi channel broadcast)
- Voice Bot
- VoIP Calling Solution
- AI Conversational Analytics (Post Call analysis with AI)

